	`gnus-treat-display-smileys' by default when XEmacs or Emacs 21 is
	running.
	(gnus-treat-display-smileys): Check for `smiley-mule' instead of
	`gnus-bitmap'.
	(gnus-article-x-face-command): Don't check for xbm for x-face-e21.

